    <p class="lede">Fisher &amp; Paykel is the New Zealand-engineered premium built-in oven brand (founded 1934 Auckland, Haier Group-owned since 2012 with NZ engineering + manufacturing retained) with a genuine LA-local parts advantage through F&amp;P USA's Huntington Beach CA distribution warehouse. Our LA F&amp;P oven service covers the full built-in lineup: <b>Series 9 Professional</b> flush-mount flagship (integrated suite aesthetic, West LA custom-kitchen concentration), <b>Contemporary</b> mainstream built-in, <b>Pyrolytic self-clean</b> signature (900°F cavity clean — F&amp;P's defining feature), <b>CombiSteam</b> hybrid steam + convection (LA hard-water descaling at 6-12 month intervals), and the pure <b>Steam Oven</b> SKU. Huntington Beach proximity means common parts arrive next-day or same-day on ~80% of F&amp;P oven calls. Same-day dispatch across LA, Orange County, Ventura County. $89 residential diagnostic, waived with repair.</p>
